---
description: Require changelog and doc sync when completing project changes
alwaysApply: true
---

When you finish a task that changes behavior, UX, architecture, or dependencies for the PoE Wiki Agent project:

1. Add a dated entry to `docs/CHANGELOG.md` (newest first) using bullets like `- Label — description`, or run `python scripts/add_changelog_entry.py "Title" "Description"`.
2. Run `python scripts/sync_docs.py` to regenerate `README.md`, `docs/architecture.html`, and `docs/changelog.html`.
3. If architecture changed, update `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` (not README or HTML directly).

Do not edit the plan files in `.cursor/plans/`.
